---
---

<section class="section section--tint s5-steps">
  <div class="container">

    <h2 class="s5-steps__heading">Your Journey to Luminous Skin</h2>

    <div class="s5-steps__grid">

      <div class="s5-steps__step">
        <div class="s5-steps__step-number" aria-hidden="true">1</div>
        <h3 class="s5-steps__step-heading">
          Personalized Skin Consultation
        </h3>
        <p class="s5-steps__step-body">
          Your experience begins with a private consultation. Our expert aesthetician will analyze your skin and discuss your goals to create a personalized treatment plan, ensuring stunning and effective results.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="s5-steps__step">
        <div class="s5-steps__step-number" aria-hidden="true">2</div>
        <h3 class="s5-steps__step-heading">
          The Regenerative Treatment
        </h3>
        <p class="s5-steps__step-body">
          In our serene treatment room, your skin is meticulously cleansed and prepped. We then use advanced, painless nano-infusion technology to deliver the potent Salmon DNA (PDRN) serum deep into your skin, ensuring a comfortable and relaxing 60-minute experience.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="s5-steps__step">
        <div class="s5-steps__step-number" aria-hidden="true">3</div>
        <h3 class="s5-steps__step-heading">
          The Luminous Reveal &amp; Aftercare
        </h3>
        <p class="s5-steps__step-body">
          You&#39;ll leave with an immediate, dewy glow and visibly hydrated skin. The regenerative benefits of PDRN will continue to work for weeks, further smoothing fine lines and refining texture. We will provide a simple aftercare plan to prolong your luminous results.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .s5-steps__heading {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-h2);
    font-weight: var(--weight-regular);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-lg);
    line-height: 1.3;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .s5-steps__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .s5-steps__step {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .s5-steps__step-number {
    width: 56px;
    height: 56px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background-color: var(--color-cta);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    font-weight: var(--weight-bold);
    color: var(--color-text);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .s5-steps__step-heading {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-h3);
    font-weight: var(--weight-regular);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .s5-steps__step-body {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .s5-steps__grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-md);
    }
  }
</style>
